title: Ganesh
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian restaurant with some vegetarian dishes, a few of which are vegan or can be made vegan. Has special sub-section in main menu. Offers both North and South Indian varieties, with options on spice level. Prices are around 110,000 vnd per main dish which is on the pricey side by local standard.
streetAddress: 57 Nguyen Dinh Chieu St, Mui Ne Beach
